"title": "1436: reality",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1436",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture provides an accurate and reliable guide to the realities of the spiritual and material worlds. It affirms the reality of human sin, of the power and purpose of God to deal with sin through Jesus Christ and of the guidance of the Holy Spirit.</p>\n<h2>The reality of God</h2>\n<h3>The reality of the existence of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:4-Job42:5\">JOB 42:4–42:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:22-2Sam7:23\">2SA 7:22–7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:23\">1KI 8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:10\">JER 10:10</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of the love of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7-1John4:9\">1JN 4:7–4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">ROM 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20-Gal2:21\">GAL 2:20–2:21</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of God's salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:20\">PSA 68:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:5\">PSA 65:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:9\">PSA 79:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:7\">MIC 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:47\">LUK 1:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11\">TIT 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of the revelation of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:4\">PSA 19:1–19:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:9\">JHN 1:1–1:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15-Acts14:17\">ACT 14:15–14:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:20\">ROM 1:18–1:20</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of knowing God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:19\">ROM 1:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:8-Gal4:9\">GAL 4:8–4:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of the word of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:160\">PSA 119:160</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:30\">PSA 18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:12\">HEB 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23\">1PE 1:23</a></p>\n<h2>The reality of sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8-1John1:10\">1JN 1:8–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:3\">PSA 58:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:1-Isa59:2\">ISA 59:1–59:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9\">JER 17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a></p>\n<h2>The reality of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>The reality of his existence</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John1:3\">1JN 1:1–1:3</a></p>\n<h3>His reality foreshadowed in the past</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:17\">COL 2:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:5\">HEB 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:1-Heb10:5\">HEB 10:1–10:5</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of his divinity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:2\">JHN 1:1–1:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:3-Rom1:4\">ROM 1:3–1:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:9\">COL 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of his humanity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:2\">MAT 4:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:3\">MRK 6:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:40\">JHN 8:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:28\">JHN 19:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22\">ACT 2:22</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of his resurrection</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:1-Matt28:10\">MAT 28:1–28:10</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:1-Mark16:8\">MRK 16:1–16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:18\">LUK 24:1–24:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:1-Acts1:3\">ACT 1:1–1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:39-Acts10:43\">ACT 10:39–10:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:8\">1CO 15:3–15:8</a></p>\n<h2>The reality of the guidance of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">JHN 14:16–14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7-John16:11\">JHN 16:7–16:11</a></p>",
